<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5829&amp;source=Test">Fortified Bellowing V</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Dance of Blades - This ability allows you to make a spinning attack that hits everything within a small radius around you.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5830&amp;source=Test">Dance of Blades I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5831&amp;source=Test">Dance of Blades II</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5832&amp;source=Test">Dance of Blades III</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Discordant Melodies - This ability causes all songs played during its duration to generate an increased amount of hate. Additional ranks increase the hate generated.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5833&amp;source=Test">Discordant Melodies I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5834&amp;source=Test">Discordant Melodies II</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5835&amp;source=Test">Discordant Melodies III</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Shield of Notes - When this ability is activated, your music forms a physical barrier about you, decreasing the damage you take from spells and melee attacks. Increased ranks improve both the effectiveness of the barrier as well as how much damage it can absorb before it fails.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5836&amp;source=Test">Shield of Notes I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5837&amp;source=Test">Shield of Notes II</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5838&amp;source=Test">Shield of Notes III</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5839&amp;source=Test">Shield of Notes IV</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=5840&amp;source=Test">Shield of Notes V</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Improved Vision - This ability permanently enhances your vision. The first rank grants you infravision, the second rank grants you ultravision, and the third rank grants you the ability to see the invisible.<br>
<br>
Delay Death - This ability increases how far below zero your hit points can fall before you die by 100 hit points per rank. You will still fall unconscious when you reach zero hit points.<br>
<br>
Healthy Aura - This ability raises the maximum that your regeneration can be increased with items and spells by 5 points per rank.<br>
<br>
Mnemonic Retention - This ability gives you an additional spell slot so you can memorize an additional spell.<br>
<br>
